the rest of this file is probably going to be the stuff i aim to add in the mod

first of, the mod takes place on a new planet, currently named Gleo but i might change it, everything is not confirmed fuck you
the plenet is always facing the sun the same way so it has 3 areas: (which probably isnt how it works irl but i dont care)

    cold area is away from the sun,
        low amount of heating and power
        expensive but strong units

    hot area
        abundance of power and heat
        more centered on liquid production and flying units.
        requires the buildings to be cooled rather than heated.

    neutral area in between.
            this area is most similar to normal gameplay on serpulo (purple planet)
            everything is balanced, kinda, not as in how good stuff is, it just means everything is mediocre
            mostly ocean with some islands

https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1TuLMvi6DSPTYfWjnsxkD1Tz2AsLHdsSdQHTxmB0rBH4/edit?gid=0#gid=0
spreadsheet with important stuff

campaign progression

    each part is kinda its own mini campaign
    1st part (middle area):
        player starts in the middle part, this progresses until around tier 3 units,
        after conquering the final enemy base the player unlocks cold & hot maps

    part 2a (cold area):
        player starts with a new tech tree
        this side has low power & stuff needs heating (basically erekir, orange planet)
        shit is expensive
    progresses until tier 4 or 5 units

    part 2b (hot area):
        player starts with a new tech tree
        this side has a lot of power but needs a lot of cooling instead
        shit is cheap but also very weak, meaning u have to go for numbers
        progresses until tier 4 or 5 units

    part 3 (back to the middle area):
        requires player to beat both part 2a & 2b
        player continues with tech from part 1, and gains new tech research based on part 2a & 2b
        later on player gets acces to nanobots, which can be used to build self healing structures units

        tier 4 & 5 units can be either normal, or specialized
        nanobot units by default are weak af and not worth it, but they can be upgraded into specialized units

        specialized units are based on part on all areas,
            cold specialized units are very expensive, but very strong with a low unit cap, specialized in ground units
            takes a good amount of time to make them

            hot specialized units are cheaper and more specialized in flying
            fast to produce, glass cannons

            neutral specialized units are not that cheap but also not expensive, specialized in water units
            mid time to produce

        extras:
            1 map for both part 2a & 2b, unlocked after beating part 3
            both maps are meand to be as a final challange for their respective planet side

        splitting campaigns
        mini campaign inside a mini campaign, has their own tech tree but can also use their parent campaigns tech tree
